{"tid":153504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"甘肅飛天韆鞦變「跳樓機」　座椅急墜地致9傷","createTime":"2017-03-12T15:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T07:38:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a091530f548b4acf7ba386a2713648c94c70c41","tid":153504,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:30:41.000Z","msg":"2017年3月11日 星期六<br />\n甘肅省隴南市西和縣石堡鄉劉城村王崖社廟會發生機動遊戲事故，飛天韆鞦瞬間變「跳樓機」！<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170311/s00004/1489201403411SL4_68741125CF9B994FB7F017ED5FD37A4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489201403411SL4_68741125CF9B994FB7F017ED5FD37A4A.jpg&h=eb4f144b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從微博上的事發短片可見，當時飛天韆鞦正在旋轉，突然間一聲巨響，全部座椅急墜下地，有遊客急跳出座椅，而圍觀群眾傳出尖叫聲。<br />\n網上消息指，9名傷者中，其中1人初步診斷為重傷，轉院至天水市第一人民醫院救治。該縣公安機關已將流動遊樂設施業主拘留接受調查。<br />\n有內地網民留言指「一直覺得這個危險系數好低，但&hellip;&hellip;以後不坐了」。亦有人稱因這機動遊戲是臨時搭建，相信正規遊樂場不會出現這事。 <br />\n（微博） <br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170311/s00004/1489201603965\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489201603965&d=wLht58ApaBOsBOdSjqbSDV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=48ead6b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170311%2Fs00004%2F1489201603965&h=9c294bb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170311/s00004/1489201603965</a>"},{"pid":"b64fb6522918e445d9cb88c2b6a9473fd1db3974","tid":153504,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1791e950a0a7585c51af8356a82de29f02607179","tid":153504,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:39:07.000Z","msg":"都冇死"},{"pid":"95e405ab084ce34fe475b058fc5fae135aad8f52","tid":153504,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63d96d9ff8a25ae80d3abd547ed363200ce83e45","tid":153504,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T16:25:30.000Z","msg":"唔驚喜，唔意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db330cbe656fb9ea7cdbf8dca33d1158058d5787","tid":153504,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T07:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}